title: Food processing vs Protein Visualization
description: Data transormations from nutrition data set to visualize the negative correlation between level of food processing and protein density in foods

title: Dual Stories in Visualization: NYPD Bias vs Fairness
description: Seeking to tell opposing stories with the same dataset.  focusing on the number of reports can tell one story, while focusing on the composition can tell another.

title: NLP Restauraunt Cuisine Identifier
description: Trained a Multinomial Logistic Regression model that achieved 81% accuracy on test set for 15-class cuisine prediction to promote customer satisfaction

title: Weather Analysis
description: Performed distributed PCA to extract seasonal modes, and clustered stations by thermal signature for interactive geospatial and temporal visualizations to detect potential utility load spikes and support resilience planning

title: Book Recommendation System
description: Developed a book recommendation system a regularized user/item-bias model with stochastic gradient descent

title: Ethics in Machine Learning for Skincare
description: Ethical considerations at each stage of development for a skincare recommendation machine learning system.

title: Biomedical Image Classifier
description: Created a convolutional neural network to classify biomedical images of cell nuclei with 98% accuracy after addressing class imbalance with data augmentation and hyperparameter tuning.
